      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUTUMN FROST (2) is a progressive type who was denied narrowly here two weeks ago with a big gap back to third. He has speed to burn and the engine to hold them off. STOKOMO (1) keeps finding one better but the form around him stacks up. He's peaking fourth-up and looks the immediate danger. SYNTHESISE (7) resumes and is a filly who will appreciate a solid tempo. Two hit-outs have her ready and she's likely to make her presence felt. TRIPOD TERROR (4) struggles to land the winning blow but a genuine tempo brings him right into the race and he can catch them late. YOU'RESOGOLDEN (8) should push forward from the inside draw with AUTUMN FROST. She's still lightly raced and improving but may be vulnerable late.",
